N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4408.3 - Quarterly reports

State Regulations

Each corporation shall file with the commission, within
15 days of the close of each fiscal quarter, a quarterly report of the
activities of the corporation in a form prescribed by the commission. The
commission may for good cause grant a reasonable extension of time for the
filing of any such report. Notes
